\c 51
\s Rwiyo rwokuchema zvivi
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi, panguva yakasvika muporofita Natani kwaari, iye apinda kuna Bhatishebha.
\p
\v 1 Ndinzwirei tsitsi, Mwari nokuda kwounyoro hwenyu; Dzimai kudarika kwangu nokuda kwengoni dzenyu zhinji.
\v 2 Ndisukei zvakaipa zvangu chose, Ndinatsei chivi changu.
\v 3 Nokuti ndinoziva kudarika kwangu; Chivi changu chinogara chiri pamberi pangu.
\v 4 Ndakakutadzirai imi, iyemi moga, Ndakaita chinhu chakaipa pamberi penyu; Kuti munzi makarurama pakutaura kwenyu, Muve usina mhosva pakutonga kwenyu.
\v 5 Tarirai, ndakaberekerwa muzvakaipa; Mai vangu vakandigamuchira muzvivi.
\v 6 Tarirai, munoda zvokwadi pamwoyo; Munoda kundidzidzisa uchenjeri mukati makavanda.
\v 7 Ndinatsei nehisopi, ndive akanaka, Ndishambidzei, ndichene kupfuura mazaya echando.
\v 8 Ndinzwisei mufaro ndive nomwoyo muchena; Kuti mapfupa amakavhuna afare.
\v 9 Vanzirai zvivi zvangu chiso chenyu, Dzimai zvakaipa zvangu zvose.
\v 10 Sikai mukati mangu mwoyo
\s wakachena, Mwari;
\s Vandudzai mukati mangu mweya wakarurama.
\s il Regai kundirasha pamberi penyu; Musabvisa mweya wenyu
\s mutsvene kwandiri.
\p
\v 12 Dzoseraizve kwandiri mufaro
\s wokuponesa kwenyu;
\s Nditsigirei nomweya, unoda.
\MO Xi‘C‘n.1&7',1k1sa vahiki nzira dzenyu;
\s Uye vatadzi vachatendeukira kwamuri.
\s la Ndirwirei pamhosva yeropa, Mwari,
\s imi Mwari muponesi wangu;
\s Ipapo rurimi rwangu ruchaimbira kururama kwenyu kwazvo.
\v 15 Ishe, zarurai miromo yangu; Ipapo muromo wangu uchaparidza kurumbidzwa kwenyu.
\v 16 Nokuti imi hamufariri zvibayiro; ndingadai ndaikupai izvo; Hamufadzwi nechipiriso chinopiswa.
\v 17 Zvibayiro zvaMwari mweya wakaputsika; Mwoyo wakaputsika nowakapwanyika, imi Mwari hamungaushori.
\v 18 Itirai Zioni zvakanaka nokuda kwenyu; Vakai masvingo eJerusaremu.
\v 19 Ipapo muchafarira zvibayiro zvakarurama, nechipiriso chinopiswa nechipiriso chinopiswa chose; Ipapo vachabayira nzombe paaritari yenyu.
